r__ThemedContainerShared-sc-14a006c2-0 fZhmhl container"><div class="header-defaults"><div class="header-defaults-wrap"><div class="rich-wrap render-rich-text"><p></p><h1>Your Next Step Starts Here.</h1><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="tint"></div></header><section class="tcc-block block-imagelist RenderBlock__ThemedRenderBlockShared-sc-a50436c1-0 fIVLQv Render__ThemedRenderShared-sc-19f89b08-0 jpNLSp layout-smartcolumns  bg-color color-alt align-default width-full block-id-eeaebff9-9797-4078-a0d7-0b9f20fee17b custom-columns in-view" data-block="true" id="32f549fc-af90-4cd7-81f7-bd10da201378"><div class="row-inner"><div data-container="true" class="Container__ThemedContainerShared-sc-14a006c2-0 fZhmhl container"><div class="row-defaults"><div class="row-defaults-wrap"><div class="rich-wrap render-rich-text"><h2>Following Jesus is a journey, and there is always a next step to take.</h2><p>Whether you are new to faith or have been walking with Jesus for years, your next step matters. These steps are designed to help you grow, find community, and live out your purpose.</p></div></div></div><div class="row-content" data-imagelist="true"><div data-list="true" class="ThemedList-sc-27f03d01-0 fsgivr widget-list smartcolumns-3 shape-square columns-three layout-smartcolumns align-default"><div data-edit-list="true"><div data-listitem="true" class="shape-square align-default layout-smartcolumns ThemedListItem__ThemedListItemShared-sc-e88acacf-0 eIYNXa"><div class="feature image"><img alt="A young man with tattoos smiles warmly as he hugs another man in an outdoor baptismal pool, surrounded by a supportive crowd in front of a modern building." src="./getInvolved6_files/_JH_5589__mediumsquare__.webp" loading="lazy" data-media-image="true"></div><div class="content"><div class="rich-wrap render-rich-text"><h4>Baptism</h4><div class="ButtonRenderer__ThemedButtonRendererShared-sc-94f0fbbc-0 jDqjoj" data-buttons="true"><a id="c30cfa89-d78c-424f-aec9-1f9b465da